## What is StreamPulse?

A production-shaped, recruiter-grade demo of a **real-time stream-discovery platform**.
It ingests viewer-count and chat-rate signals from live streams across Twitch, YouTube,
Kick, and TikTok; computes a per-stream **viral score** every second using a weighted
blend of leading indicators; and surfaces a natural-language **"why this is trending"**
narrative powered by an LLM (Groq · Llama 3.1).

> Open the demo, click **Start Live Demo**, and watch a stream spike from "steady" to
> "VIRAL" with the score, sparkline, alert feed, and AI explanation all updating in
> real time.

---

## Recruiter pitch

- A **time-series feature pipeline**, an **anomaly detector**, a **weighted scoring
  engine**, an **LLM explanation service**, and a **WebSocket alert dispatcher** —
  all wired into a single dashboard with sub-second updates.
- Designed and built end-to-end: types, scoring math, server, frontend, animations,
  failure modes, system-design write-up.
- Falls back to an in-browser simulator when the backend is offline so the link
  always works on a recruiter's first click.
- Includes a guided **6-step Recruiter Demo** that explains the architecture in under
  60 seconds.

[**→ See the system-design write-up**](https://streampulse-ai.vercel.app/case-study)

