## Folder structure

```
apps/
  web/                    Next.js 15 frontend
    app/
      page.tsx            Live dashboard (Viral Moment Engine)
      architecture/       System design page
      case-study/         Engineering write-up
      api/
        explain/          /api/explain — Groq proxy for stream narratives
        insight/          /api/insight — Groq proxy for aggregate insights
      watch/[movieId]/    Sample video player
    components/viral/     Stream cards, badges, charts, tour
    lib/
      viralEngine.ts      scoring + tier + ranking helpers
      viralSim.ts         in-browser pipeline simulator
      sampleStreams.ts    seeded fake streams
  api/                    Fastify backend (optional, deploys to Render)
packages/shared/          Wire-format types shared across runtimes
```

